body.name: Double Stroller Organizer for Bob Duallie and Baby Jogger City Mini GT Black
deliveryMessages: $4.99 delivery Wednesday, February 21. Order within 10 hrs 39 mins.
FREE pickup Wednesday, February 21. Order within 21 hrs 39 mins
features: Specifically designed for the Bob Duallie and City Mini GT by Baby Jogger. It will NOT work with the City Mini Double as it has a bar in the middle of the handlebar. Holds more then just water bottles! Great for Disneyland. Do NOT buy this item for a Booyah Stroller.

If your buying this for a stroller other then the ones it is designed for then do your measurements. Organizer is 23 inches long (25 inches with inner straps) to fit inside the 26 inch handlebars. If your inner dimensions are less then 26 inches this organizer will NOT work. If your handlebar is smaller with a 20-21 inch opening please look up item B01DCZHLC4. This item may fit better.
Will fit double wide strollers with and OPEN handlebar (no bar in the middle). Front net for keys, phones, wallet etc.
Multi-sectioned pockets for water bottles, food, etc. (jewelry, keys, etc).
Insulated center console for large items. (diapers, wipes, sippy cups and bottles)
body.description: Overall dimensions 23 x 4.5 x 9 inches Middle compartment is insulated and is 8 x 4.5 x 9 inches deep. Easily fits multiple diapers and wipes in the compartment. Large enough to hold and insulate up to 6 water or baby bottles.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2017
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best double stroller organizer out there
reviews.reviewText: This double stroller organizer is the best one for my double bob. I wish I had found it months ago when I started looking for one. I think this is my 2nd or 3rd attempt at a double stroller organizer that would not just carry my drinks, but essentials that I don't want to keep in the bottom of the stroller since we store it outside on our porch.It's incredibly functional. The pockets are wide and large and deep. It held my coffee cup with no problems. However I did put a circular coaster underneath where I put my drink and that may have helped. In the middle pocket I keep all of our diapers and wipes and bibs. The outer Pockets just have essentials for me like lotions and sunblock, lip gloss, Kleenex, gum, that sort of stuff.Beyond all the great things about this organizer [ there are no cons for me, only Pros] i think the best part is that it straps on in 4 different places. So I can't imagine it sagging anywhere, which was a huge problem with other organizers. I can't stress enough that this is probably the best double stroller organizer out there. Do not waste your money on other products.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 29, 2017
reviews.reviewText: Very happy with this. It's huge and holds a ton. My only picky complaint is that there's not much to hold cups upright. Our other consoles have round designated cup holders and this has kind of a dividing piece of fabric in the large side pockets. It's great if you have a large cup, but if you have a small one, it doesn't really keep it upright. It's fine if your cup seals up, but if it doesn't you have to watch it. All in all though this is a great product and holds a ton. I also like how stable and non saggy you can make it because there are so many Velcro straps.
Overall good purchase, spacious, fits City Mini GT Double stroller, well-designed. Deducting a star because the material is a bit scratchy and cheap.

Fits perfectly on my Baby Jogger City Mini GT Double Pram.The functionality surpasses any other caddy I've seen on the market. It fits 2 kids water bottles in the pockets so easily. There's sleeves for you to pop a coffee cup into it to keep it secure. And spots for your phone. Then there's the deep insulated pocket. I'm so glad I read the reviews and decided to go with the one slightly more expensive. There's 6 points to secure the caddy onto. So doesn't matter so much the angle of my handles. Sooo great! Highly recommend

This organizer is amazing!! PERFECT for our BOB duallie! The pockets are huge and the cooler is really big too. We can fit about 3 bottles, a cooler pack and a few other items in the cooler portion of this organizer. Makes it so much easier when kids want a cold snack or baby needs bottle that's cooled, we don't have to dig through the bottom storage portion of the stroller anymore. I have been searching for something similar to this for a long time, i'm surprised it is not more popular and easy to find! The cooler portion makes this soooo worth it!
